          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>gnocchi</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the gnocchi for 3 min or until it begins to rise to the top of the pot</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>gnocchi</strong></p>",
