    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained gnocchi</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and mix in with the<strong> squash sauce</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> spinach & garlic mushrooms </strong>and <strong>torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
